Hi %11, we welcome you to Fishers Life.

Just arrived at the motel in Palm Beach, you can turn on the light of the room by looking at the switch and by pressing the "Space" bar.

To get out of your room, just take the room key in your inventory. To do this use the "E" key and select the "Inventory" option, on the right you can select the key and take it in your hand. Then go to the door and perform the action "Open / Close Door" using the "Spacebar" when you scroll to the "Door" option.

To store the key in your inventory, you can use the "E" key and select the "Put Back" option.
Leave your motel room and head over to the garage and go to Elk City to take the Garbage or Delivery man jobs!

The fuel station is limited! It is the players who refuel the pumps.

To refuel the station, a tutorial is available on our website.

Know that you will need:
-A 4X4.
- A trailer "Drill".
- A truck.
- A trailer tank.

If the station is empty, you can go in the store inside to buy a Jerrycan. Know that the price is very high compared to the jerrycans that you will find at the Silverton supermarket.

You can also make jerrycans by using empty jerrycans and by ordering oil at import-export!
Go to our website to watch the specific tutorial on how to make gas!

Here you can take a car out of your garage! When you have a house, you can take it out of your own garage. But in the meantime use these garages!

You can open the vehicle by looking at the door handle.

To start the vehicle, look in first person to the right of the steering wheel, this is the red button.

The headlights are on the left of the steering wheel.

You can store clothes in the trunk of your car, do not worry it will be saved!
Go to Elk City to work as a garbage man or delivery man!

You're probably hungry, to eat you just go to your Inventory by holding the "Windows" key and take the food.

Once you take the food in your hand, you can eat it by clicking "Eat" in the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key)

You can buy food at the supermarket. If not, you will have to make it at the food factory or buy it from other players!
Think of eating from time to time or you may pass out!

You are definitely thirsty, to drink you just go to your Inventory by holding the "Windows" key and take the drink.

Once you take the drink in your hand, you can drink it by clicking on "Drink" in the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key)

You can buy a drink at the supermarket. If not, you will have to make it at the food factory or buy it from other players!
Remember to drink from time to time or you may pass out!
You have received your salary. You can sign your paycheck by going to the nearest bank.
Think about getting your paycheck from time to time!

You can see the injuries you have received and your blood level in the medical menu. To access it, click on "Open Medical Menu" in the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key).

You have several types of injuries, according to these you will have to consult a doctor at the clinic.

You can buy bandages, medications ... at the general store.

To treat yourself, you will have to click on where the injury is located.

Next, click on the type of injury on the right and select the object with which to treat the injury.
Remember to go buy bandages at the general store!

To repair your vehicle, you must take the repair wrench from your Inventory (By holding the "Windows" key).

Once you have it in your hand, look at the vehicle and perform the action "Repair Vehicle" at the door.

You can buy repair wrenches at the supermarket if any is in stock, otherwise go to the goods factory to make it!
Think about buying or making repair wrenches!

The phone allows you to do a lot of things! You can add contacts, send messages, call and even request an Uber!

You can buy one or more SIM cards from the telephone company.
Ask the number of your relatives to stay in touch with them!

Twitter is the place to advertise or look for work. Do not hesitate to discuss freely with the people around you on this beautiful social network.

Different commands are available, you can consult them by typing "/ h" on Twitter.
Do promotion for your business, search for work or recruit people to help you!

Businesses allow you to sell whatever you want at the price you want! Give your business a name and rent the premises for the time you want! A point on the map will be displayed to all players with the name of your business.

To sell an item, you just have to put it on the ground and do the Sell action to be able to sell it. Configure the price and the name!
Think about promoting your business on Twitter!

The factories are very important. As you can see, there are several items that you can make.

To make the items in question, you must have materials that you can find by mining or buying them from other players who sell it! There is also a manufacturing time depending on what you want to make.

You can store things in your factory so you do not lose anything if you do not have a home! />
Once you have made your items, you can rent a business to sell what you want at the price you want!
Think about recruiting people to help you during the manufacturing process! Also think about going to import-export, see if there are any materials you would need!

The vehicle parts factory allows you to manufacture parts to build vehicles! This is where you will create the parts you need to make your car.

You can then sell vehicles you've built to a dealer business in Silverton, Northdale, Elk City or Stoney Creek.
Get help to build your vehicle!

Here you can buy a map that will show you where the minerals are. You will have to look in this area where are the minerals, know that even if the area disappears, you can continue to search!

When you arrived in the area, search the soil via the wheel of interaction by clicking on "Inspect the soil"
Generally, the areas are 600 feet from the center and near a road. Do not forget to buy a shovel and a pickaxe in the mining shop!

You managed to prospect an area! When you have found the area and you have prospected, you must mark the position of the ore.

Then take your shovel and dig to find the ore. Once you have finished digging, take your pick and mine.
You can sell the diamonds at the Northdale Gem Store!

With this trade, you will be able to go to the various stores indicated on the map in order to secure the shop against the possible robber!

You will have to go towards the cash register and select the action "Securing Store" via the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key)
You will earn money by securing the stores!
With this trade, you will be able to make fish burgers to sell to people! Know that you will have to make your materials, you have a cooking plate in the kitchen to cook everything!
To assemble hamburgers, go to the manufacturing menu in the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key)!
With this job, you can make fish tacos to sell to people! Know that you will have to make your materials, you have a cooking plate in the kitchen to cook everything!
To assemble hamburgers, go to the manufacturing menu in the interaction wheel (By holding the "Windows" key)!

You became a Real Estate Agent! You can now sell people's homes! Here is how it works:

- The owner sells his house.
- The real estate agent concludes the sale and sets his commission.

Promote your agency right now!
Welcome to your new home! You can now get out and store your vehicle in the garage, you can also furnish your house by making or buying furniture!
You will need a trailer to transport the furniture!

Here you can import materials for money or export to earn money! You will have to wait for the boat that arrives every 15 minutes to take the materials.

You can climb in the cranes and unload the containers to make a small ticket!
Think about buying less expensive players!

To access this shop you must have the "Motorhead" perk

You will have many advantages like being able to personalize license plates, change the materials of the vehicle ....
Get the Motorhead perk on www.arma3fisherslife.com

You've became a farmer! Go to the store next door to buy seeds or go directly to a field to pick up by using the interaction wheel (By holding the key "Windows").

When you have planted the seeds, pick them up and go to the food factory to see what you can do!

You can rent greenhouses so that no one can steal your crops. To rent, go to the door of the greenhouse and rent it by holding the key "Windows" and selecting the option "Rent Greenhouse".
Go to a Greenhouse or a Field!

Here you can become a repairman to help people! But that's not all, the work is not limited to repairing vehicles, you can also impound them and repair the broken objects of the car!

To put a vehicle in the impound:
-Construct a tow truck.
-Return to the location of the repair / tow.
-Lift the ramp with the button in the passenger compartment of the vehicle. > -Place the vehicle at the ramp.
-Select the action that is at the vehicle hitch at the bottom of the ramp.

To repair an object of the map:
- Go near a broken object.
-Select the "Windows" key and perform the "Repair" action.
Go to the factory to make your tow truck!

To hunt you must equip yourself at the hunting store by taking a gun, loaders and tags!

Attention, a license is required but you can very well hunt without!

When you have to find animals, kill them and skin the bodies to recover meat.

You can label the meat according to the needs, for that, put the meat on the ground and take the label in your hand.

Then go to the food factory to make food!
Here you can buy marijuana seeds to start making dirty money. You can sell the cannabis to the pirate ship by finding its location.
Find the location of the pirate ship by going to see the treasurer! For marijuana, you will need the following equipment: a table, a planter, a lamp, a fan, a grinder and a weight!
Here you will be able to find clues about illegal positions against dirty money. Illegal positions never change places except for the moving boat.
Find the drug dealer to start making dirty money!

The vehicle factory allows you to make vehicles.

You can then sell the vehicles you've built to a dealer business in Silverton, Northdale, Elk City or Stoney Creek. />
To build a vehicle, you will need parts, you can get some by selling stolen vehicles or building them!
Steal a vehicle or get help from other players!
This store has a stock! You can add stock to earn some money making the items this NPC sells! If there is no more stock, you can always try to buy what you need from a player.
You can now fish in the depths of Fishers Island! Buy a net and throw it into the water!

The garbage worker allows you to make a solid money base, it is not huge, but it will help you get started.

Take the garbage worker job by approaching the NPC and performing the action "Start / Stop Work Garbageman".

The outfit will be provided to you and a truck will be delivered to you outside.

Get in the vehicle and look at your map the location of the different bins.

The postman job allows you to make a solid money base, it's not huge, but it will help you get started.

Start by taking the postman job by approaching the NPC and performing the action "Start / Stop Delivery Work".

The outfit will be provided to you and a truck will be delivered to you outside.

Unlock the vehicle and open the back door (Chest), for information, you can crouch to go to the bottom.

Go to a package and perform the action "Check the shipping label" to know where you have to deliver the package. The position will be indicated on the map. When you arrive at the place of delivery, take the package in your hand by performing the action "Move".
Head to the place of delivery.

Bowling is our favorite recreational activity! You can come, accompany, and enjoy a unique system!

To play, you must register at the counter at a track with another person, you can not play alone.

Once you are registered on the track, start the game and go to the chosen track.

Take the bowling ball in your hand and hold "E" to throw it .
Head to the track and start playing!
